reviewText: I dislike the dvd and I didn't get anything from it at all. Because it didn't give me what I read about it. Was a total waste of money and really no romance at all just a lot of massage which I can do that.
I looked at them and got some good ideas to use with the man in my life. Can't wait to use it.
You watch 2 people rubbing each other's back, arms and legs (EACH arm and leg).  No technique for giving a good massage was given! Very unprofessional video!

This is a bundle of a few videos that I bought.

I give them a solid 4.

They're loaded with informaton but don't have the glitz of a TV infomercial which is fine with me.  I just like to get down to business and learn.

They sometimes use pretty techical terms but they do come back and explain everything.

I didn't get everything the first time I watched it but that's why I got the DVDs.  I'll be watching as a refresher from time to time.
This is a pretty good video set.  Have done business with them before so I know the videos would be filled with solid instruction.
I didn't watch this personally but I bought them for my sister along with a couple other videos.  She said she was really happy with them.
I really like this video.  Ive purchased a bunch with mixed results but this is one of the better ones....

This DVD was the worst $40 I've ever spent.  The video only shows someone giving the other person a massage slowly for an hour.  Still can't figure out what they thought was sensual about it.  I learned absolutely nothing and wish I could send it back for a refund.
